vote.title: Authorize (1) the adoption of a Resolution of Support for Express Development, Inc. and/or its affiliate(s) (Applicant), related to its application to the Texas Department of Housing and Community Affairs for 9% Housing Tax Credits for the development The James at Wheatland to be located at 7100 West Wheatland Road, Dallas, Texas 75249 (Project); and (2) an agreement with the Applicant for a line of credit in the amount of $500.00 for the proposed multifamily development - Not to exceed $500.00 - Financing: General Fund
